## MCP Tool Parameter Reference

The harness builds `payload.request` for you — pass it directly without modification. This section documents every field so you understand what you are passing and can verify correctness.

---

### Tool 1: `retrieve_memory_by_chunks`

Called at stage `need_mcp_retrieve_memory_by_chunks`.

**How to call it:**
```
retrieve_memory_by_chunks(payload.request)
```

**Full parameter shape (`payload.request`):**

```json
{
  "schemaVersion": "1.0",
  "requestId": "<unique string — auto-generated by harness>",
  "taskId": "<task ID from session>",
  "requirementIntent": {
    "taskType": "<string — e.g. 'ui-change', 'api-change', 'refactor'>",
    "domain":   "<string — optional, domain scope>",
    "module":   "<string — optional, module scope>",
    "feature":  "<string — optional, feature scope>",
    "hardConstraints": ["<string>", "..."],
    "riskSignals":     ["<string>", "..."]
  },
  "retrievalChunks": [
    {
      "chunkId":   "<string — unique within this request>",
      "chunkType": "<CoreTask | Constraint | Risk | Pattern | SimilarCase>",
      "text":      "<string — optional, the retrieval query text for this chunk>",
      "structuredScopes": {
        "domains":  ["<string>"],
        "modules":  ["<string>"],
        "features": ["<string>"],
        "layers":   ["<string>"],
        "concerns": ["<string>"],
        "repos":    ["<string>"],
        "services": ["<string>"],
        "symbols":  ["<string>"]
      },
      "taskShape": {
        "taskType":          "<string>",
        "featureShape":      "<string>",
        "engineChangeAllowed": true,
        "likelyLayers":      ["<string>"],
        "riskSignals":       ["<string>"],
        "complexity":        "<string — optional>"
      }
    }
  ],
  "searchProfile": {
    "activeOnly":           true,
    "minimumAuthority":     "<Draft | Observed | Reviewed | Approved | Canonical>",
    "maxItemsPerChunk":     5,
    "requireTypeSeparation": true
  }
}
```

**Field notes:**
| Field | Required | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `schemaVersion` | yes | Always `"1.0"` |
| `requestId` | yes | Unique per call; harness auto-generates |
| `taskId` | yes | From the session |
| `requirementIntent.taskType` | yes | String describing the task category |
| `requirementIntent.hardConstraints` | yes | May be empty array |
| `requirementIntent.riskSignals` | yes | May be empty array |
| `requirementIntent.domain/module/feature` | no | Scope filters; omit if unknown |
| `retrievalChunks[].chunkId` | yes | Must be unique within the request |
| `retrievalChunks[].chunkType` | yes | One of: `CoreTask`, `Constraint`, `Risk`, `Pattern`, `SimilarCase` |
| `retrievalChunks[].text` | no | The free-text query for this chunk |
| `retrievalChunks[].structuredScopes` | no | All sub-arrays may be empty |
| `retrievalChunks[].taskShape` | no | Only for `SimilarCase` chunks |
| `searchProfile.minimumAuthority` | yes | Harness defaults to `Reviewed` |

